      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i am looking at houses for the first time and im kinda confused about mortgage types. can u explain the difference between a fixed rate mortgage and an adjustable rate mortgage (arm)? specifically i want to know how the monthly payments might change over the first 5 years if i go with the arm instead of the fixed one.",
